---
import Button03 from "./Button03.astro";
---
<div class="deltag">
<h1>DELTAG I KAMPEN MED OS</h1>
<p>Besøg vores videnscenter og bliv inspireret af hvad du kan gøre af store og små ting som alle gør en kæmpe forskel for vores natur og havmiljø.</p>
</div>
<div id="grid_1-1-1-1">
    <div id="s01"><div class="box"><p>Hvad kan du gøre?</p><a href="#">Gode Råd</a></div></div>
    <div id="s02"><div class="box"><p>Deltag i kampen</p><a href="#">Bliv Plastic Changer</a></div></div>
    <div id="s03"><div class="box"><p>Gør en forskel</p><a href="#">Bliv Erhvervspartner</a></div></div>
    <div id="s04"><div class="box"><p>Kom med udenfor</p><a href="#">Ryd op i Naturen</a></div></div>
</div>
<div class="button">
<Button03 />
</div>
<style>
#grid_1-1-1-1 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
margin-left: 1.2%;
}

.button {
    margin-top: 3%;
    margin-bottom: 3%;
    text-align: center;
}

.deltag {
        margin-left: 5%;
        margin-top: 5%;
        margin-right: 50%;
        margin-bottom: 3%;
    }

    .deltag h1 {
        margin-bottom: 3%;
        font-size: 50px;
    }

    #s01 {
    background-image:
    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(245, 246, 252, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.73)),
    url("../Assets/grid01.png");
    width: 95%;
    height: 500px;
    background-size: cover;
    color: white;
}

#s02 {
    background-image:
    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(245, 246, 252, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.73)),
    url("../Assets/grid02.png");
    width: 95%;
    height: 500px;
    background-size: cover;
    color: white;
}

#s03 {
    background-image:
    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(245, 246, 252, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.73)),
    url("../Assets/grid03.png");
    width: 95%;
    height: 500px;
    background-size: cover;
    color: white;
}

#s04 {
    background-image:
    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(245, 246, 252, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.73)),
    url("../Assets/grid04.png");
    width: 95%;
    height: 500px;
    background-size: cover;
    color: white;
    
}

.box{
    margin-top: 400px;
    margin-left: 5%;
}

.box p {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: rubik;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.box a{
    font-size: 28px;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: rubik;
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
    #grid_1-1-1-1 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
        align-items: center;
justify-items: center;
gap: 10px;
margin-left: 0%;
margin-right: 0%;
    }

    .box {
        margin-top: 70%;
    }


    .box a{
       font-size: 18px;
    }

    #s01, #s02, #s03, #s04  {
        width: 200px;
height: 200px;
border-radius: 5%;
    }

    #s03, #s04 {
        margin-top: 5%;
    }

    .deltag {
        margin-left: 5%;
        margin-top: 5%;
        margin-right: 20%;
        margin-bottom: 3%;
        font-size: 16px;
    }

    .deltag h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

}

</style>